                  <summary>The recto contains the beginning of a Coptic contract between Georgios and Petros starting with the opening formula, 'anok pason,' pointing to a provenance at the Apa Apollo monastery of Bawit. The verso contains 1 line with part of the address mentioning the name of the monk as Georgi[os.</summary>
